The paper discusses automating deep learning model selection using autoencoders, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method is also applicable in scenarios where there are distributed data sources, which could fall under the categories of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), computer vision (cs.CV), and natural language processing (cs.CL).
